name: TSAL-Waterloo
tagline: These are the EAGLE files that I made to create the Tractive System Active Light
body:
### Authors and Contributors
Wesley McCloy created these files with the help of Carl Engelmann and based it off: **Marc-Andre Vaillancourt**: *Circuit detecteur de haute tension pour une voiture electrique* (2011) [A link to the report](https://code.google.com/p/tsalivd/)


***

### Support or Contact
Please email me at info@wesleymccloy.com if you have any questions, I am very willing to help you with your project
